➜Silverlight 3正式发布
https://www.solidot.org/story?sid=12279	3360
微软<a href="http://www.osnews.com/story/21806/Silverlight_3_Released">发布</a>了<a href="http://www.microsoft.com/silverlight/resources/install.aspx">Silverlight 3</a>，它强力推销的Flash替代。Silverlight 3运行平台为Windows和Mac OS X 10.4.8+，支持Internet Explorer 6/7/8，Firefox 2/3，和Safari 3/4。<i>主要的<a href="__SLASHLINK__" sect="developers" sid="09/03/19/0211248" sn="article" tid="32">新特性</a>包括：GPU硬件加速，支持H.264、AAC、MPEG-4等新编解码器，raw bitstream Audio/Video API，改进了日志，支持720P流视频，多触摸支持，库缓存支持等等。</i>微软还针对开发者发布了<a href="http://www.microsoft.com/downloads/details.aspx?displaylang=en&amp;FamilyID=2050e580-f1d5-4040-bb09-e6185591b6b5">Silverlight 3 SDK</a>和<a href="http://www.microsoft.com/downloads/details.aspx?displaylang=en&amp;FamilyID=9442b0f2-7465-417a-88f3-5e7b5409e9dd">Silverlight 3 Tools</a>。
