https://www.solidot.org/story?sid=12296	57600
Unkown 写道<i> "<a href="https://sourceforge.net/community/cca09/vote/">投票地址点击这里</a>。大家为自己喜欢的开源项目助威吧！话说回来，最重头的Best Project奖里的候选项目都不如Best New Project和Best Project For Academia里的让人鸡冻。"</i>